      "title": "3 hours power cuts for next two days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) has approved 3-hour power cuts from July 4 and 5.",
        "Accordingly, 1 hour and 40 minutes of power shedding will be imposed during the daytime and 1 hour and 20 minutes during the night for the ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW groups.",
        "Two hours and 30 minutes of power shedding will be imposed for Group CC from 6.00 am to 8.30 am while 3-hour power cuts for groups MNOXYZ from 5.30 am to 8.30 am."
      ],
